# Keep this file intentionally minimal.
#
# For `wrangler pages deploy ./dist`, Wrangler falls back to `.gitignore`
# when `.wranglerignore` is missing. Our `.gitignore` excludes `node_modules`,
# which incorrectly drops Expo-exported web assets under:
#   dist/assets/node_modules/*
#
# Having this file prevents that fallback so all files in `dist/` are uploaded.
